  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to lxqt-sudo</title>

    <para>
      The <application>lxqt-sudo</application> package is a graphical front
      end to <application>sudo</application> and <application>su</application>
      respectively.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

